title: FASH Professional makeup Brush Set,12 pc, For Eye Shadow, Blush, Eyeliner,eyebrow....
description: Add style to your makeup collection with FASH's 12 Essential makeup brushes. It comes in a very trendy copper gold colored faux leather pouch. A complete collections - contains all necessary brushes for face, eye and lip make up. The perfect brush set for your professional and personal needs which will give a flawless finish to your makeup application and gives you that stunning look you always wanted. Not only this, we are sure once you buy this you will forget others. The bristles are feathered soft specially designed for your precious skin. It is a perfect brush set for your favorite FASH Eye shadow Palette.Here is what's included :1. Large Powder Brush: Ideal to apply compact powder & bronzer application of the cheekbones & temple area.2. Blush Brush: Used to apply blush onto the face, primarily on the cheekbones.3. Foundation Brush: Used to apply any kind of foundation be it liquid, cream or solid more evenly.4. Eye shadow Brush: Used to apply powder & cream shadows to eyelids.5. Concealer Brush: Ideal to apply concealer under the eyes, helps cover blemishes & skin tone.6. Blending Brush: Blend multiple eye shadow shades.7. Medium Angled Shading Brush: Brow highlighting or blend the crease.8. Angled Eyeliner Brush: Apply eyeliner deep into the lash line.9. Pencil Brush: Smudges color on the upper & lower lash line.10. Eyeliner Brush: Apply a smooth, even-thin line of eye liner on the upper or lower lash lines.11. Mascara Brush: Apply mascara-separation & exactness of Lashes.12. Eyebrow & Eyelash Comb: Combs eyebrow hair & helps to separate lash hair thus removing mascara clumps.
